WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:05.820 --> 00:00:11.450
<i>The Hellhorde and Imperial Army have been 
locked in battle for many years.</i>

3
00:00:11.940 --> 00:00:15.150
<i>Led by their grand inquisitor, 
Torture Tortura,</i>

4
00:00:15.460 --> 00:00:18.650
<i>the Hellhorde's elite inflict 
their torture on a daily basis.</i>

5
00:00:18.650 --> 00:00:23.410
<i>She faces fierce beasts, flames, 
unknown devices and spells,</i>

6
00:00:23.410 --> 00:00:26.330
<i>yet the princess does not give in.</i>

7
00:00:26.330 --> 00:00:28.240
<i>She would never give in.</i>

8
00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:32.220
<i>She would never let the words, 
"I surrender!" leave her lips so readily.</i>

9
00:00:32.930 --> 00:00:38.680
<i>Meanwhile, the princess's former friend, 
the assassin Sakura Heartrock,</i>

10
00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:44.690
<i>fails to assassinate the Hell-Lord, 
and sets off on a new path.</i>

11
00:00:56.440 --> 00:00:59.900
Sakura-chan, 'tis finally time 
for your first torture.

12
00:00:59.900 --> 00:01:01.820
Will you really be okay on your own?

13
00:01:01.820 --> 00:01:05.550
Yes. I feel like I'd lean 
on your help with you there.

14
00:01:06.010 --> 00:01:08.500
Okay, time to give it my all.

15
00:01:11.010 --> 00:01:14.770
<i>I've committed a lot 
of terrible deeds in my past.</i>

16
00:01:15.550 --> 00:01:17.270
<i>So to make amends...</i>

17
00:01:18.270 --> 00:01:19.700
<i>from here on out...</i>

18
00:01:21.610 --> 00:01:24.500
I'll make people happy through torture!

19
00:01:24.930 --> 00:01:26.000
What?

20
00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:35.100
Princess?

21
00:03:04.200 --> 00:03:05.950
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

22
00:03:06.780 --> 00:03:07.910
Ex.

23
00:03:08.600 --> 00:03:10.630
I've made up my mind.

24
00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:13.730
I will never give in to their torture!

25
00:03:13.730 --> 00:03:15.330
Man, if I haven't heard that before.

26
00:03:15.720 --> 00:03:18.130
This time, I'm dead serious.

27
00:03:18.130 --> 00:03:20.960
Which is why I'm giving you this.

28
00:03:21.480 --> 00:03:22.970
A lightning amulet.

29
00:03:22.970 --> 00:03:26.490
This allows you to activate 
a lightning spell with your mind.

30
00:03:26.930 --> 00:03:30.140
The moment you think, "Her Highness 
is gonna cave to the torture,"

31
00:03:30.140 --> 00:03:30.710
What?

32
00:03:30.710 --> 00:03:33.190
you can fire a lightning spell at me.

33
00:03:33.190 --> 00:03:37.190
Agh

34
00:03:34.290 --> 00:03:37.010
The pain will help me 
regain my composure...

35
00:03:37.010 --> 00:03:38.420
I've calmed down.

36
00:03:38.420 --> 00:03:40.990
and I'll be able to 
hold off on surrendering.

37
00:03:40.990 --> 00:03:43.710
Is that the only way 
you can control yourself?

38
00:03:45.210 --> 00:03:48.270
Where'd this thing come from, anyway?

39
00:03:48.270 --> 00:03:51.360
After a torture the other day, 
while we were on a stroll,

40
00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:54.030
I got a tour of the Hellholm armory.

41
00:03:54.030 --> 00:03:56.270
A tour of their armory 
in the middle of a stroll?!

42
00:03:56.270 --> 00:03:57.750
For an enemy nation's princess?!

43
00:03:57.880 --> 00:04:02.510
Hmph

44
00:03:59.110 --> 00:03:59.870
Hmph!

45
00:03:59.870 --> 00:04:02.500
Just goes to show how much they trust me!

46
00:04:02.850 --> 00:04:05.410
That's when I secretly 
borrowed the amulet.

47
00:04:05.410 --> 00:04:07.470
Betraying their trust...

48
00:04:11.130 --> 00:04:12.960
You're sure about this?

49
00:04:12.960 --> 00:04:14.930
Yeah, go ahead.

50
00:04:14.930 --> 00:04:17.920
Do I have it in me, though?

51
00:04:17.920 --> 00:04:21.060
To fire a lightning spell 
at Your Highness?

52
00:04:21.260 --> 00:04:22.750
Rest assured.

53
00:04:22.750 --> 00:04:26.870
After making up my mind, 
I won't be folding so easily.

54
00:04:31.830 --> 00:04:33.130
Princess.

55
00:04:34.180 --> 00:04:36.040
'Tis time for torture.

56
00:04:36.570 --> 00:04:39.270
This will be your torture for today...

57
00:04:40.150 --> 00:04:41.420
Fried chicken.

58
00:04:41.420 --> 00:04:43.130
Looks yummy!

59
00:04:47.250 --> 00:04:49.720
I-Is something wrong, Princess?

60
00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:52.560
N-No, not at all.

61
00:04:53.110 --> 00:04:54.940
Nice going, Ex.

62
00:04:54.940 --> 00:04:56.910
I was able to stay strong, thanks to you.

63
00:04:56.910 --> 00:04:58.350
Glad to hear it.

64
00:04:58.580 --> 00:05:02.690
You were going on like, 
"Do I have it in me?"

65
00:05:02.690 --> 00:05:04.590
Yet you didn't hesitate to activate it.

66
00:05:04.590 --> 00:05:07.720
I, too, was surprised 
at my complete lack of resistance.

67
00:05:08.240 --> 00:05:10.400
Are you really okay?

68
00:05:11.330 --> 00:05:13.120
Don't worry about me.

69
00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:16.520
Perhaps you should ask 
the same of yourself.

70
00:05:16.520 --> 00:05:19.620
You're right, I <i>do</i> love fried chicken.

71
00:05:19.620 --> 00:05:20.550
However...

72
00:05:21.030 --> 00:05:23.790
Do you know which piece is my favorite?

73
00:05:24.070 --> 00:05:28.640
Verily, fried chicken comes 
in a variety of pieces.

74
00:05:28.960 --> 00:05:31.500
The thigh, popular for 
its fatty dark meat.

75
00:05:32.050 --> 00:05:35.070
The wing, with its chewy 
eating experience.

76
00:05:35.740 --> 00:05:38.740
And more, all with their own appeal.

77
00:05:38.740 --> 00:05:41.680
But the piece that you're most fond of...

78
00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:43.090
'Tis none other than...

79
00:05:43.930 --> 00:05:44.770
The drumstick!

80
00:05:44.770 --> 00:05:45.910
You got it!

81
00:05:50.970 --> 00:05:53.310
What in the world has 
been going on today?

82
00:05:53.650 --> 00:05:56.000
Don't worry about it...

83
00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:58.350
You're right on the money.

84
00:05:58.350 --> 00:06:00.840
I love drumsticks.

85
00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:03.290
The way they look gets me so excited.

86
00:06:04.210 --> 00:06:07.220
It <i>is</i> the shape you 
associate most with chicken.

87
00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:10.610
Incidentally, the meal 
that I purchased today

88
00:06:10.610 --> 00:06:13.240
happened to contain only 
a single drumstick.

89
00:06:13.630 --> 00:06:14.530
In other words...

90
00:06:14.980 --> 00:06:20.100
After I eat this one, 
there will be no drumsticks left.

91
00:06:21.110 --> 00:06:23.470
W-Wait, I give in. I'll talk!

92
00:06:25.660 --> 00:06:27.660
This is for Her Highness's sake!

93
00:06:27.660 --> 00:06:31.270
I will steel my heart 
and carry out my duty to the end!

94
00:06:31.270 --> 00:06:32.900
You monster!

95
00:06:32.900 --> 00:06:36.710
Wh-What is this, Princess? 
You're glowing!

96
00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:40.330
<i>Th-This is the strongest strike so far!</i>

97
00:06:40.330 --> 00:06:42.920
<i>I feel like I'll pass out 
if I drop my guard!</i>

98
00:06:42.920 --> 00:06:47.930
<i>However, I'm the Princess and 
Commander of the Imperial Third Legion!</i>

99
00:06:47.930 --> 00:06:49.750
<i>A measly lightning strike like this...</i>

100
00:06:54.220 --> 00:06:57.370
Cannot stop me from surrendering!

101
00:06:55.310 --> 00:07:02.310
Surrender by Might

102
00:06:58.200 --> 00:07:01.980
Try using that iron willpower 
to endure the torture instead!

103
00:07:02.850 --> 00:07:05.690
The princess
confessed

104
00:07:08.200 --> 00:07:09.920
Delicious!

105
00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:12.010
Drumsticks are the best!

106
00:07:12.010 --> 00:07:14.200
They just scream "chicken" to me!

107
00:07:14.460 --> 00:07:17.170
Would you like to try 
the other pieces, Princess?

108
00:07:17.170 --> 00:07:19.210
Really? Awesome!

109
00:07:19.480 --> 00:07:22.150
I love fried chicken!

110
00:07:25.660 --> 00:07:30.170
It's imperial custom to eat egg 
dishes around the end of the year.

111
00:07:32.470 --> 00:07:35.800
Makes you wonder how it got started.

112
00:07:36.220 --> 00:07:40.060
I've also bought the items you asked for.

113
00:07:40.960 --> 00:07:42.650
With biscuits?

114
00:07:42.650 --> 00:07:47.150
Of course, and vanilla 
ice cream to go with them.

115
00:07:49.260 --> 00:07:52.770
You must be a mind reader.

116
00:07:55.200 --> 00:08:03.210
'Tis Time for "Torture,"Princess

117
00:07:55.450 --> 00:08:00.470
<i>Torture planned to use 
the leftover chicken for rice pilaf,</i>

118
00:08:00.470 --> 00:08:02.410
<i>but there was none left in the end.</i>

119
00:08:08.540 --> 00:08:11.550
<i>An experimental spell went haywire...</i>

120
00:08:12.130 --> 00:08:17.090
<i>splitting up Torture into good 
and evil personalities.</i>

121
00:08:19.500 --> 00:08:23.920
Right now, my good self is trying 
to find a way to turn us back.

122
00:08:24.260 --> 00:08:28.280
So for today's torture, it'll be me,

123
00:08:28.510 --> 00:08:30.860
the evil Torture, who's in charge!

124
00:08:31.440 --> 00:08:34.400
Time for your torture, Princess!

125
00:08:34.400 --> 00:08:37.470
Your evil self still shows up 
for work, huh?

126
00:08:37.470 --> 00:08:39.630
I'm not really sure what makes her evil.

127
00:08:39.630 --> 00:08:42.240
For today's torture...

128
00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:44.910
Straight out of a plastic bag?!

129
00:08:44.910 --> 00:08:47.080
The Torture I know would never do that!

130
00:08:47.430 --> 00:08:49.670
So this is evil Torture!

131
00:08:49.670 --> 00:08:52.460
Pretty low bar for "evil," 
don't you think?

132
00:08:52.460 --> 00:08:57.490
Do you really think I'd yield 
to such slapdash torture?

133
00:08:58.450 --> 00:08:59.870
Take a look!

134
00:08:59.870 --> 00:09:01.750
This is your torture!

135
00:09:01.750 --> 00:09:02.980
An éclair!

136
00:09:04.930 --> 00:09:06.060
Your Highness!

137
00:09:06.440 --> 00:09:09.990
Number one... It's number one...

138
00:09:10.490 --> 00:09:14.500
There are all sorts 
of great pastries out there,

139
00:09:14.500 --> 00:09:20.010
but taking everything into account, 
like taste, availability, and price...

140
00:09:20.450 --> 00:09:23.360
The number one, tried-and-true pastry 
that won't let you down...

141
00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:25.500
is a convenience store éclair!

142
00:09:25.890 --> 00:09:29.800
That light, crispy dough, 
thickly coated in chocolate...

143
00:09:30.120 --> 00:09:33.260
And filled with a rich, gooey custard!

144
00:09:33.260 --> 00:09:35.410
Perfect in every way!

145
00:09:35.410 --> 00:09:38.060
You may be evil, but 
you're still Torture!

146
00:09:38.060 --> 00:09:40.050
It's the perfect torture!

147
00:09:40.050 --> 00:09:40.960
Huh?

148
00:09:40.960 --> 00:09:43.980
I don't think she feels 
as strongly as you do.

149
00:09:44.630 --> 00:09:47.000
I want it... I want to eat it!

150
00:09:47.420 --> 00:09:49.110
However!

151
00:09:49.450 --> 00:09:53.370
I'm the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion!

152
00:09:53.370 --> 00:09:55.690
I will not give in to your torture!

153
00:09:55.690 --> 00:09:57.900
I will not crave that éclair!

154
00:09:57.900 --> 00:09:59.890
Yeah! You tell her, Your Highness!

155
00:09:59.890 --> 00:10:01.280
What are you talking about?

156
00:10:01.280 --> 00:10:02.210
What?

157
00:10:02.210 --> 00:10:05.450
I got one for you, too, 
so let's enjoy them together.

158
00:10:05.450 --> 00:10:06.490
Huh?

159
00:10:06.490 --> 00:10:09.400
You'll give it to me even though 
I haven't surrendered?

160
00:10:09.400 --> 00:10:10.510
What about the torture?

161
00:10:10.510 --> 00:10:11.870
Oh, right.

162
00:10:11.870 --> 00:10:14.830
I'm supposed to get 
a secret out of you for the torture.

163
00:10:16.880 --> 00:10:18.520
Well, whatever.

164
00:10:18.520 --> 00:10:19.890
"Well, whatever?!"

165
00:10:19.890 --> 00:10:22.200
Didn't I say I'm the evil Torture?

166
00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:24.630
My feelings come before the rules.

167
00:10:24.940 --> 00:10:27.980
And nothing beats sharing some 
good food with other people!

168
00:10:27.980 --> 00:10:31.000
E-Evil Torture!

169
00:10:31.840 --> 00:10:33.900
Time to eat!

170
00:10:36.940 --> 00:10:38.170
Yummy!

171
00:10:38.170 --> 00:10:39.570
This is great!

172
00:10:39.570 --> 00:10:41.450
The chocolate's not too sweet, either!

173
00:10:41.450 --> 00:10:43.310
It's so gooey!

174
00:10:43.410 --> 00:10:46.330
The 
Next Day

175
00:10:47.730 --> 00:10:53.040
I managed to return to normal, 
but my head still hurts from yesterday.

176
00:10:54.550 --> 00:10:58.960
My evil self technically 
wrote up a report...

177
00:10:58.960 --> 00:11:00.840
but it's completely incoherent.

178
00:11:02.220 --> 00:11:05.100
Dear Usual Torture

179
00:11:03.060 --> 00:11:04.240
A letter?

180
00:11:05.180 --> 00:11:08.350
The evil Torture said
she didn't need it,
but since the éclair was good,
here's a secret for you.

181
00:11:06.340 --> 00:11:08.350
<i>Dear usual Torture,</i>

182
00:11:08.700 --> 00:11:11.570
<i>The evil Torture said she didn't need it,</i>

183
00:11:11.570 --> 00:11:14.980
<i>but since the éclair was good,
here's a secret for you.</i>

184
00:11:15.570 --> 00:11:19.480
<i>All clownfish are born as males.</i>

185
00:11:20.590 --> 00:11:22.170
How honorable of her.

186
00:11:22.770 --> 00:11:25.090
Thank you, Princess.

187
00:11:26.110 --> 00:11:28.570
I may not be able to remember it...

188
00:11:28.570 --> 00:11:30.590
but I seem to have had fun as well.

189
00:11:28.580 --> 00:11:32.000
"Torture" Report Form

190
00:11:28.580 --> 00:11:32.000
It was totally
 awesome

191
00:11:34.730 --> 00:11:37.470
Looks like you're back 
to your usual self, Torture.

192
00:11:37.470 --> 00:11:40.620
Allow me to apologize 
for the inconvenience.

193
00:11:40.620 --> 00:11:42.860
Still, I've had enough.

194
00:11:42.860 --> 00:11:46.630
Why are all of these 
experimental spells going haywire?

195
00:11:46.630 --> 00:11:49.620
Actually, there's a reason for that.

196
00:11:49.620 --> 00:11:51.800
What, you're here to make excuses?

197
00:11:51.800 --> 00:11:53.980
Go ahead, let's hear them.

198
00:11:54.970 --> 00:12:01.490
Currently, Hellhorde R&D is experimenting 
with treating lumbago via electrotherapy.

199
00:12:01.490 --> 00:12:07.290
But a lightning amulet they were using
has gone missing from the armory,

200
00:12:07.290 --> 00:12:11.170
leading to calibration issues that
have resulted in these frequent errors.

201
00:12:11.960 --> 00:12:12.800
What?

202
00:12:13.770 --> 00:12:15.210
A what amulet?

203
00:12:15.590 --> 00:12:17.540
'Tis a lightning amulet.

204
00:12:20.540 --> 00:12:21.340
Ah.

205
00:12:22.420 --> 00:12:27.390
So it's not as though R&D is 
frivolously causing all this mayhem...

206
00:12:27.390 --> 00:12:31.150
U-Um, uh, well...

207
00:12:31.150 --> 00:12:33.560
Excuse me, I've been paged.

208
00:12:33.560 --> 00:12:36.600
I'll be back when 'tis time 
for your torture, Princess.

209
00:12:43.230 --> 00:12:45.600
I think it'd be best if you apologized.

210
00:12:47.530 --> 00:12:49.990
The princess
apologized

211
00:12:52.950 --> 00:12:55.000
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

212
00:12:55.590 --> 00:12:59.430
<i>I've committed a lot 
of terrible deeds in my past.</i>

213
00:13:00.040 --> 00:13:01.760
<i>So to make amends,</i>

214
00:13:03.050 --> 00:13:04.380
<i>from here on out...</i>

215
00:13:06.150 --> 00:13:09.020
I'll make people happy through torture!

216
00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:10.580
What?

217
00:13:17.310 --> 00:13:19.580
Princess?

218
00:13:21.470 --> 00:13:24.790
Wait, is that you, Sakura?

219
00:13:25.270 --> 00:13:27.950
Sakura? The Sakura that we know?

220
00:13:27.950 --> 00:13:31.920
I'm sure of it,  although it was hard to 
tell at first with that outfit...

221
00:13:32.250 --> 00:13:34.640
Sakura, you...

222
00:13:45.220 --> 00:13:46.790
You're alive?

223
00:13:52.350 --> 00:13:53.560
What a relief.

224
00:13:55.670 --> 00:13:58.150
Why, Princess?

225
00:14:00.850 --> 00:14:04.200
I was deceiving you the whole time!

226
00:14:05.440 --> 00:14:07.150
I could tell.

227
00:14:07.150 --> 00:14:08.870
Your attack that day...

228
00:14:09.830 --> 00:14:13.940
It was a strike full of hesitation 
that lacked your usual commitment.

229
00:14:15.310 --> 00:14:17.100
That told me everything.

230
00:14:18.790 --> 00:14:22.250
I knew that deep down, 
you didn't want to kill me.

231
00:14:23.170 --> 00:14:27.070
I could see it in your eyes.

232
00:14:27.640 --> 00:14:29.550
That you had no choice in the matter.

233
00:14:31.050 --> 00:14:33.970
It was the same for me.

234
00:14:36.630 --> 00:14:38.320
I didn't have a choice in the matter.

235
00:14:39.500 --> 00:14:40.480
Which is why...

236
00:14:41.650 --> 00:14:44.730
I'm so relieved to see 
that you're alive and well.

237
00:14:45.600 --> 00:14:47.070
Princess...

238
00:14:47.800 --> 00:14:49.690
Thank you.

239
00:14:50.800 --> 00:14:54.450
Yes. I had no choice in the matter.

240
00:14:55.650 --> 00:15:00.190
That said, I truly 
enjoyed our time together.

241
00:15:01.620 --> 00:15:03.570
All that time, I couldn't 
help but think...

242
00:15:09.170 --> 00:15:14.070
How nice it'd be 
if we were really friends.

243
00:15:15.760 --> 00:15:17.430
Sakura.

244
00:15:19.070 --> 00:15:20.480
I've also always...

245
00:15:23.040 --> 00:15:24.170
Your Highness?

246
00:15:24.910 --> 00:15:25.890
No.

247
00:15:27.190 --> 00:15:29.560
Let's see if you can get 
the rest out of me.

248
00:15:30.300 --> 00:15:32.940
You're an inquisitor now, aren't you?

249
00:15:33.650 --> 00:15:36.870
Show me what you can 
do with your torture!

250
00:15:40.850 --> 00:15:42.090
Yes!

251
00:15:48.040 --> 00:15:53.010
<i>We may have had a painful past, 
but now things are different.</i>

252
00:15:53.970 --> 00:15:55.710
<i>We're no longer from rival nations.</i>

253
00:15:56.320 --> 00:15:58.630
<i>I'm just a prisoner, 
and she's my torturer.</i>

254
00:15:59.250 --> 00:16:04.210
<i>There's nothing strange about a prisoner 
and her torturer being friends.</i>

255
00:16:05.260 --> 00:16:07.270
<i>Isn't that right, Sakura?</i>

256
00:16:08.190 --> 00:16:10.340
That's amazing, Sakura!

257
00:16:11.030 --> 00:16:12.700
Did you practice that a lot?

258
00:16:13.060 --> 00:16:18.280
After a torture, you're supposed to 
complete a report immediately after.

259
00:16:18.830 --> 00:16:22.510
But I'll make an exception this once 
and give her an extension.

260
00:16:25.030 --> 00:16:27.460
<i>The princess talked.</i>

261
00:16:28.310 --> 00:16:31.860
<i>Just her and Sakura, late into the night.</i>

262
00:18:04.970 --> 00:18:09.980
Hellholm Happy Farm

263
00:18:05.510 --> 00:18:11.570
Still, I never imagined you were 
the one Sakura had failed to assassinate.

264
00:18:11.570 --> 00:18:13.470
I sure was surprised.

265
00:18:13.870 --> 00:18:15.910
I'm sorry, Sakura-chan.

266
00:18:15.910 --> 00:18:16.980
Oh, no.

267
00:18:16.990 --> 00:18:20.950
Hellholm Happy Farm

268
00:18:16.990 --> 00:18:20.950
Petting Zoo

269
00:18:17.250 --> 00:18:20.450
I'm to blame as well 
for omitting the details.

270
00:18:20.930 --> 00:18:24.580
Well, I'm sure there's 
a lot we still have to talk about...

271
00:18:24.580 --> 00:18:27.090
But let's forget all that for today...

272
00:18:27.090 --> 00:18:29.220
and have fun at the farm!

273
00:18:27.120 --> 00:18:35.340
Hellholm Happy Farm
 Petting Zoo

274
00:18:29.220 --> 00:18:32.890
<i>To celebrate the princess 
and Sakura's reconciliation,</i>

275
00:18:32.890 --> 00:18:35.330
<i>they're taking a group trip to a farm.</i>

276
00:18:35.330 --> 00:18:36.620
Your Highness!

277
00:18:36.620 --> 00:18:38.900
Don't run off in excitement
or you might trip!

278
00:18:38.900 --> 00:18:40.760
I know!

279
00:18:54.180 --> 00:18:55.700
A goat!

280
00:18:55.700 --> 00:18:57.090
So cute.

281
00:18:57.090 --> 00:18:59.890
This is my first time at a farm.

282
00:18:59.890 --> 00:19:01.770
Mine as well.

283
00:19:01.770 --> 00:19:06.790
The empire's not without farms,
but they have handlers to do all the work.

284
00:19:06.790 --> 00:19:08.170
Everyone.

285
00:19:08.170 --> 00:19:10.630
They're selling animal food over there.

286
00:19:10.630 --> 00:19:12.030
I wanna feed them!

287
00:19:12.750 --> 00:19:15.620
Here's some food for you.

288
00:19:15.850 --> 00:19:17.640
Feel free to take more.

289
00:19:18.800 --> 00:19:20.170
Is it good?

290
00:19:22.330 --> 00:19:24.170
They're so adorable!

291
00:19:25.730 --> 00:19:28.800
Huh? You're not gonna 
feed them, Princess?

292
00:19:28.800 --> 00:19:33.320
Well, I never even looked 
after my own steed.

293
00:19:33.750 --> 00:19:37.830
So I don't have any experience 
feeding large animals.

294
00:19:38.310 --> 00:19:41.880
I'm a little scared now that 
I've come face-to-face with them.

295
00:19:41.880 --> 00:19:42.640
What?

296
00:19:43.320 --> 00:19:44.640
How pathetic.

297
00:19:44.640 --> 00:19:45.580
Hey!

298
00:19:45.580 --> 00:19:47.420
Oh, I'm sorry!

299
00:19:47.420 --> 00:19:50.580
Now that I can be honest with you, 
I blurted out how I really feel!

300
00:19:50.580 --> 00:19:52.110
That's how you feel about me?!

301
00:19:53.100 --> 00:19:55.620
H-Hey, I can do it, too!

302
00:20:20.150 --> 00:20:23.650
Hands-On Milking

303
00:20:33.180 --> 00:20:35.000
You're good at this, Sakura.

304
00:20:37.460 --> 00:20:38.510
How was it?

305
00:20:39.150 --> 00:20:41.100
It was my first time...

306
00:20:41.490 --> 00:20:44.460
But it was warm, squishy, and fuzzy!

307
00:20:44.460 --> 00:20:46.510
Squishy and fuzzy?!

308
00:20:48.480 --> 00:20:49.780
You're right!

309
00:20:49.780 --> 00:20:51.900
It's squishy and fuzzy!

310
00:20:51.900 --> 00:20:54.670
Squishy 'n' fuzzy!

311
00:20:53.080 --> 00:20:55.010
Your Highness, your face! Your face!

312
00:21:01.820 --> 00:21:03.520
This milk's amazing!

313
00:21:03.520 --> 00:21:05.540
You can really tell that it's fresh.

314
00:21:05.540 --> 00:21:06.950
So creamy!

315
00:21:08.740 --> 00:21:11.190
It really is delicious.

316
00:21:13.040 --> 00:21:17.920
Soft-Serve Ice Cream
Made with Fresh Milk

317
00:21:13.040 --> 00:21:17.920
Pork-Wrapped 
Rice Balls

318
00:21:13.210 --> 00:21:17.920
They have a store that sells soft-serve 
ice cream using the same milk.

319
00:21:17.920 --> 00:21:20.180
I'd love to try it, but...

320
00:21:20.180 --> 00:21:23.950
It's a little too chilly out 
to be eating soft serve.

321
00:21:23.950 --> 00:21:25.400
I want some!

322
00:21:26.370 --> 00:21:28.880
Maomao-chan's full of energy!

323
00:21:29.330 --> 00:21:31.990
Let me go and buy some, then.

324
00:21:31.990 --> 00:21:33.990
Who here wants some soft serve?

325
00:21:38.270 --> 00:21:40.170
I do, too, of course.

326
00:21:42.740 --> 00:21:44.300
This is great!

327
00:21:44.300 --> 00:21:46.710
It's so rich and creamy.

328
00:21:48.280 --> 00:21:52.440
Huh? Sakura-chan, you tried 
to assassinate Princess-chan?

329
00:21:52.440 --> 00:21:53.660
Yes...

330
00:21:53.660 --> 00:21:55.690
She even got a slash in.

331
00:21:55.690 --> 00:21:57.370
Huh...

332
00:21:57.370 --> 00:22:00.900
Pretty wild. I mean, you two 
are friends now, right?

333
00:22:04.710 --> 00:22:07.210
Yeah! Friends!

334
00:22:07.210 --> 00:22:08.500
Awesome!

335
00:22:08.500 --> 00:22:09.610
Mm-hmm.

336
00:22:10.480 --> 00:22:12.260
Big news, everyone!

337
00:22:13.060 --> 00:22:15.720
It looks like there's 
a giant maze over there!

338
00:22:15.720 --> 00:22:17.260
I was the one who found it.

339
00:22:17.260 --> 00:22:19.030
Let's all go check it out!

340
00:22:19.030 --> 00:22:19.850
Yeah!

341
00:22:19.850 --> 00:22:21.390
We can't skip out on that!

342
00:22:21.400 --> 00:22:25.400
Maze Adventure

343
00:22:21.680 --> 00:22:23.830
Get a move on!

344
00:22:41.330 --> 00:22:45.210
They're all
 great friends

345
00:22:46.690 --> 00:22:49.870
Sakura... Sakura.

346
00:22:50.670 --> 00:22:52.130
Sakura.

347
00:22:55.060 --> 00:22:56.260
We're here.

348
00:22:56.710 --> 00:22:58.690
Huh? Oh...

349
00:22:59.480 --> 00:23:00.580
Good morning.

350
00:23:01.980 --> 00:23:03.700
Good morning, Sakura-chan.

351
00:23:03.700 --> 00:23:06.060
I slept like a baby.

352
00:23:06.060 --> 00:23:08.110
We <i>did</i> play lots today!

353
00:23:08.110 --> 00:23:11.490
Yeah, you were out like a light.

354
00:23:11.490 --> 00:23:12.390
Take a look.

355
00:23:14.420 --> 00:23:16.940
Asleep and completely defenseless!

356
00:23:16.940 --> 00:23:20.110
Not very assassin-like of you.

357
00:23:20.570 --> 00:23:23.590
Like you weren't asleep, too. 
You just happened to wake up first.

358
00:23:23.590 --> 00:23:25.210
Hey! You-chan!

359
00:23:25.210 --> 00:23:28.110
I got a photo of her. Look.

360
00:23:28.110 --> 00:23:28.880
What?

361
00:23:30.260 --> 00:23:31.190
You're right!

362
00:23:31.190 --> 00:23:33.200
In-chan!

363
00:23:34.010 --> 00:23:37.140
Not very commander-like of you.

364
00:23:38.470 --> 00:23:41.650
Ugh, I can't believe I was drooling!

